{"tid":395604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大學民主牆】仲可以點玩？今日貼「修改45條普選」 明日貼「修改1條獨立」","createTime":"2017-09-11T02:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T10:18:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2db41b53afe2563ca6aeb200c59edf94e31c385e","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"今日貼「要求修改基本法第45條普選！」<br />\n<br />\n有無人撕? 有無人會話違反基本法？ 無！<br />\n<br />\n好啦，既然無反對，咁聽日就係正下方貼「要求修改基本法第1條香港獨立！」<br />\n<br />\n拿, 兩條標語, 分別只係要求修改既基本法條文唔同<br />\n<br />\n基本法又係可以修改既, 支那憲法都可以修改<br />\n<br />\n有乜理由只撕一條, 只係一條「犯法」, 而另一條無呢?<br />\n<br />\n單係比記者影兩日相, 已經夠撚狗撚一個SEM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8913c2527a13aa0368845fa19e2eabe26081db6","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:38:11.000Z","msg":"基本法係當年共匪同李柱銘呢堆廢老傻閪寫出黎<br />\n<br />\n無經公投, 無經立法會審議條改, 所以係好垃圾, 好多BUG係入面<br />\n<br />\n呢個只係其中一個BUG, 已夠玩一個SEM"},{"pid":"5f48ab33a52b6a3194f45e63b4ec49b38322fdbf","tid":395604,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"留名等看傻仔出手貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 花生花生"},{"pid":"93adcdd0e4b1ac37d62ae04f05f5d22fb50fc006","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等看傻仔出手貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 花生花生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪好驚呢?<br />\n<br />\n真係玩得死你架"},{"pid":"40edc30a385b9eba5acd7b8e8ed22d9181be1198","tid":395604,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無啲除咗學生都有得做既事？唔想學生孭哂"},{"pid":"2f4e11c2ee1bd7412882957d791a2cd2a43597d4","tid":395604,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c160a32d799a299ac8949cdab6e4112d31bc94c4","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無啲除咗學生都有得做既事？唔想學生孭哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜大學民主牆理論上要係學生先貼得<br />\n<br />\n如果我仲未畢業, 我一早狗衝去貼啦<br />\n<br />\n真係玩撚殘基本法個BUG, 支那狗柒出世界, 笑一世架"},{"pid":"a69a3350d9844133aca1bbf9c6bd04313fb47402","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樓主仲唔快啲去貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我畢左業嘛, 屌你"},{"pid":"793eb1925b7c7b2381d46f763f53fbb5881c1862","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57c0d6caea57e206a32379a3930f39fdbecd8d8","tid":395604,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"今日：要求取消基本法第二十二條<br />\n翌日：要求取消基本法第一條"},{"pid":"a7693e056bc85eec782eea615ee613a5e631acee","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日：要求取消基本法第二十二條<br />\n翌日：要求取消基本法第一條</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535787889c83d3389b472d03b256a377de8a64aa","tid":395604,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:06:06.